"work_id": 84157, "role": "producer", "role_id": 1089, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 1813488, "title": "JFK: Director's cut; Beyond JFK: the question of the conspiracy (S) (Captioned)", "work_id": 84987, "role": "producer", "role_id": 1089, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 868820, "title": "JFK: Director's cut; Beyond JFK: the question of the conspiracy (S) (Captioned)", "work_id": 84987, "role": "production company", "role_id": 941, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 2614708, "title": "JFK: Director's cut. Beyond JFK: the question of the conspiracy", "work_id": 84157, "role": "production company", "role_id": 941, "is_primary": true}], "also_known_as": "", "date_of_birth": null, "date_of_death": "", "genders": [{"id": 9, "name": "Male", "slug": "male"}], "languages": [], "places_of_operation": [{"id": 1, "name": "United States of America", "slug": "united-states-of-america"}], "biography": "Alexander Kitman Ho (Chinese: 何傑民; pinyin: Hé Jiémín; born 1950), known as A. Kitman Ho, is an American film producer.\n\nHe was born in Hong Kong, and emigrated with his family to the United States when he was 5 years old. He grew up in New York City's Chinatown neighborhood. After graduating from Goddard College in Vermont with a master's degree in Cinema. He continued his studies at New York University's Tisch School of the Arts.Ho has produced many of Oliver Stone's films, such as Platoon, Wall Street, Talk Radio, Born on the Fourth of July, The Doors, JFK, and Heaven & Earth. Source: Wikidata; 01/08/2023", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2025-02-26T20:21:36.424567+11:00", "external_links": [{"id": 3483, "uri": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A._Kitman_Ho"}], "uuid": "ae3a2e43-37ed-415a-9de8-4d079a04e26f", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "14601", "external_references": [{"id": 26458, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q19501850"}, {"id": 27080, "source": {"name": "VIAF", "slug": "viaf"}, "source_iden